name: Planet B Kyanite
description: Planet B Kyanite is the planet of communication and self expression. This planet cuts through fears and blockages, helping to speak one's truth. It opens the throat chakra. There are high vibrations, free from toxic energies here, it is pure and cleansing on this planet. Here one can access their mind while expanding their unique psychic abilities. This planet includes LED changing colored lights, and it glows differently under UV light, regular light, and no light. twitter:@yanachka23 instagram:@yanagordinart
